    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Neckwear consisting of two white, downward-hanging bands of fabric. These are typically worn as part of the professional regalia of lawyers, judges, and university professors.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
